<br>
EQ is a limited game, like any other.  It's good at what it is, which only goes so far.  When you get bored with EQ you need to go find something else to do, not try to completely change what you are already doing into something else.  That isn't going to solve anything.<br>
<br>
Not that I mind you speculating on these boards if you want to, Intra, but I'd suggest if you want to do something completely different for a while, try doing something *completely different*.  Bridge is a fun and challenging game.  And no, I'm not joking. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Play EQ because you like EQ.  Anything else is a disservice to yourself.<br>
